{
  "stem": "13469.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So now I found out why they had these roadblocks.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, I just remember that they had the roadblocks and that, every time you went past the roadblocks, you had to pronounce the names of various Dutch towns, like [SPEAKING DUTCH].",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And nobody except a Dutchman could pronounce those, you see.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Germans couldn't pronounce that at all.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that's how they find out which were infiltrators, saboteurs, Fifth Columnists.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We just had been with those roadblocks for a while because it was great fun to hear everybody say it, and especially when they found somebody who couldn't say it kind of thing.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- but we didn't realize, really, exactly what it was, why it was, until I recently read all this about these Fifth Columnists and saboteurs.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We, we would see, obviously, they were trying to catch Germans.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But all the ones we could see coming out of the sky, they say that a lot of them were dressed in ordinary street clothes and not in uniforms.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But we couldn't see.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were too far away from us, really, to be able to see whether they were in uniform or whether they were in [NON-ENGLISH] kind of thing.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, he probably wouldn't have got through the roadblocks.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But he stayed at home, I should think, or didn't go then, yeah.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He wasn't so good.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My mother picked it up quite well.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And, and, us kids, of course, we had no difficulties with it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We can-- we can still speak it now without an accent.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But yes, he, he wasn't quite so good on the language.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You're right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Interesting question, kind of thing-- yeah, you ask a lot of interesting questions I haven't really thought about-- more food for thought, but-- yes.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
